{"tid":1403330,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"6月-8月戰役資料整合，有料請入。","createTime":"2019-08-03T18:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T04:52:59.000Z","uid":46632,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9ecdbea490d994a1309773362d4092dee801ee2a","tid":1403330,"uid":46632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:31:27.000Z","msg":"大家好，小弟我呢就係半歷史撚嚟嘅（自修），想話喺呢個時候整合一下6月-8月嘅重大戰役或事件（包括政府同藍絲）。講就有知己知彼，但係審視歷史亦同樣重要，我唔想再見到任何義士收傷，為防止下一次嘅犧牲，我決定盡自己全力去做好份表。<br />\n<br />\n利申：自己都有D但係料唔係好夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，想請求一啲資料去同歷史做對比，不論大小都收。又或者有相關tg gp 可以邀請我都得。<br />\n<br />\n資料可以send 比: neverforgivewhywefight@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會係收到料後盡快起稿，多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023fd68f9eef33d863d8844c65557fb65cca35c4","tid":1403330,"uid":46632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:31:54.000Z","msg":"唔該大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617cf425058cceec5f5cf0cff300ff55f6025e72","tid":1403330,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:32:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"940408770d0d747815fb5c5c04a2649ad3b518c7","tid":1403330,"uid":46632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:32:58.000Z","msg":"係受，唔小心打錯字sry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c48eed79ac26d303a0c893281b21432002a5c0d","tid":1403330,"uid":46632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T18:34:36.000Z","msg":"唔該你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgm